---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="孙亚冬">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="profile-card">
        <div class="avatar">👋</div>
        <h1>孙亚冬</h1>
        <p class="tagline">AI 安全工程师 · 安全运营专家</p>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-row">
            <span class="label">微信</span>
            <span class="value">Sunarius</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-row">
            <span class="label">公众号</span>
            <span class="value">孙亚冬的内省地</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="certificates">
          <h3>专业认证</h3>
          <div class="cert-list">
            <span class="cert-item">CISSP</span>
            <span class="cert-item">PMP</span>
            <span class="cert-item">NPDP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="content">
      <section class="intro">
        <p>
          你好，我是孙亚冬，目前主要关注 <strong>AI 安全工程化</strong>、<strong>安全智能化平台</strong>、
          <strong>DLP 数据防泄漏</strong>、<strong>SOC 安全运营自动化</strong> 等方向。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="experience">
        <h2>关于我</h2>
        <p>
          拥有 6 年左右安全研发与安全运营相关经验，曾先后在安全厂商、创业公司和甲方企业中参与或主导过
          XDR/SOC 平台研发、安全资产治理、安全运营体系建设、办公安全体系建设、DLP 智能化、
          自研 SOC 平台以及 AI Agent 在安全场景中的落地实践。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mission">
        <blockquote>
          如何把复杂、重复、依赖经验的安全运营工作，转化为可平台化、可自动化、可评估、
          可持续迭代的智能安全系统。
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section class="interests">
        <h2>职业方向</h2>
        <div class="interest-list">
          <div class="interest-item">
            <span class="title">AI for Security</span>
            <span class="desc">利用大模型、Agent、RAG、Workflow 等技术提升安全运营效率</span>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-item">
            <span class="title">安全智能化平台</span>
            <span class="desc">围绕 SOC、SOAR、DLP、告警分析、威胁情报、资产治理等场景构建平台能力</span>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-item">
            <span class="title">DLP 数据安全治理</span>
            <span class="desc">关注企业数据外发、敏感信息识别、规则体系优化、智能化研判与闭环处置</span>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-item">
            <span class="title">AI Agent 安全工程化</span>
            <span class="desc">关注 Agent 编排、工具调用、权限控制、结构化输出、评估体系与可观测性</span>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-item">
            <span class="title">企业安全体系建设</span>
            <span class="desc">办公安全、云安全、终端安全、零信任、EDR、审计、SDL 与安全运营流程建设</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="career">
        <h2>工作经历</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
              <h3>某保险经纪公司</h3>
              <span class="period">2024.06 - 至今</span>
            </div>
            <p class="role">办公安全负责人</p>
          </div>
          <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
              <h3>北京未岚科技有限公司</h3>
              <span class="period">2022.09 - 2024.06</span>
            </div>
            <p class="role">安全工程师 / 项目经理</p>
          </div>
          <div class="job">
            <div class="job-header">
              <h3>深信服科技股份有限公司</h3>
              <span class="period">2020.06 - 2022.08</span>
            </div>
            <p class="role">研发工程师 / 项目经理 · XDR / SOC 方向</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
    display: flex;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  /* 左侧边栏 */
  .sidebar {
    flex: 0 0 240px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .profile-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .avatar {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666666;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-row:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #999999;
  }

  .value {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .github-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .github-link:hover {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* 证书区域 */
  .certificates {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .certificates h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #999999;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .cert-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cert-item {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* 右侧内容 */
  .content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333333;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .intro strong {
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #999999;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .experience p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #666666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mission {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .interest-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .interest-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .interest-item .title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .interest-item .desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #666666;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .job {
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .job:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .job-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .job h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #999999;
  }

  .role {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* 移动端适配 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    main {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .sidebar {
      flex: none;
      position: static;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .profile-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .job-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
